<h2>The site that does what it says on the cover!</h2>
<p>
Whether you like reading chick lit or literary classics, books have something for everyone.

</p>
<p>
We have created the 'Get Jersey Reading' website to encourage you to pick up a book you might not have thought to read and let others know what you think of it.
</p>
<p>
It's easy to sign up and get started. Simply fill in your email and password details, let us know your age and then choose a book. The more books you read and rate, the better our website will be at suggesting other books you might also enjoy.
</p>

<p>
So what are you waiting for? If you can't think of where to get started then take a look at some of our suggested reading lists.
</p>
<p>
Happy Reading
