<h2>Jersey Festival of Words</h2>
<p>Connections: The Jersey Festival of Words is a five-day literary event aimed at promoting a love of the written and spoken word across the island. The Festival will feature over 20 internationally renowned writers, 30 local writers and poets, a schools programme, writing workshops, competitions and much more.</p>
<p>It is taking place September 30th to October 4th 2015. You can download a full <a href="http://www.jerseyfestivalofwords.org/programme/">timetable</a></p>

